      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The MS/MS feature data are assumed to be in .mgf (mascot generic format) format, where each entry should have a unique feature identifier, a precursor mass to charge ratio, and spectral data in the form of one or more mass to charge ratio and intensity value tuples.",
