      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "In this paper, we introduce specXplore, an interactive Python dashboard aimed at facilitating spectral data exploration in a flexible and local network topology tailored fashion... The dashboard makes use of a two-dimensional t-distributed stochastic neighbor embedding (t-SNE) overview network of the full pairwise similarity matrix as a jumping board for localized data exploration.",
      "asbval:note": "Verbatim presence: specXplore confirmed as orchestrating tool for t-SNE coordinate generation and dashboard visualization.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1021-acs-analchem-3c04444",
