      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "For the wheat data set, the pipeline preprocessing time was less than 15 min (on a MacBook Pro laptop with Apple M1 Pro processor 2021)... Spectral data from .mgf files was loaded into the preprocessing jupyter notebooks and processed into a specXplore session object (see illustrative example notebooks https://github.com/kevinmildau/specxplore-illustrative-examples).",
