      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The processing workflows and intermediate data structures used by specXplore are built upon a cohort of open-source software Python data science packages, namely, matchms, MS2Query, ms2deepscore, spec2vec, kmedoids, Cython, numpy, pandas, scikit-learn, and scipy.",
